# Mobile Scope

> Source: `docs/architecture.md` § mobile, `docs/product.md` mobile policy

## Official app only

`mobile/MiAyudaTIC-Mobile/` — **never** extend `mobile_flutter/MBO_ULT/`.

## Auth & API

- Bearer JWT in SecureStore — no cookies
- `EXPO_PUBLIC_API_URL` — never hardcode prod host
- Standalone install: `cd mobile/MiAyudaTIC-Mobile && pnpm install`

## Roles on mobile

- `funcionario` + `tecnico` — in scope
- `lider` — **blocked** at app layer (web only)

## Field UX

- Photo report < 3 taps
- Reconnect socket with backoff after cold start / JWT expiry
- Multipart per `docs/architecture.md` § Mobile API integration

## Verify

```bash
cd mobile/MiAyudaTIC-Mobile && pnpm typecheck
```

## Skill

Invoke `.cursor/skills/mobile-field-ux` for solicitud and field screens.

## Server changes

Require Product Engineer Platform handoff — do not edit `server/` from mobile workstream.
